text: Teluk Ramunia Teluk Ramunia is a town in Kota Tinggi District, Johor, Malaysia. It is a well-known bauxite mining town in the early days of Malaysia. It is a sight seeing place, good for a family picnic spot. Now it is known for Oil and Gas Fabrication industries. ==References== ==External links== *Towns and Cities in Malaysia Category:Towns in Johor
